<title>Change CAPI Language</title>
<context ID_LANGUAGE />

In a CAPI data entry application, you can change the question language at any time.

Press <b>Ctrl+L</b> or from the <b>Options</b> menu, select <b>Change CAPI Language</b>. A dlialog box will come up to allow you to select question and help text from among the available languages.
